replies.body:
Since your friend is seeing the Bug Splat error where she can send a report, I'd suggest checking out our [**Bug Splat Guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201761974#section-mac) for some potential fixes. This might be an issue where their admin settings are conflicting with league whenever they try to play normal matches.

If your friend already has a ticket open, it would be best to wait for their reply, since our tech guys will be able to go much more in depth. If they haven't gotten a reply yet, shoot me that ticket number and I'd be more than happy to check up on that!
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
